dataset_id: IceBridge UAF Lidar Profiler L1B Geolocated Surface Elevation Triplets V001
title: IceBridge UAF Lidar Profiler L1B Geolocated Surface Elevation Triplets V001
summary: This data set contains surface profiles of Alaska Glaciers acquired using the airborne University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF) Glacier Lidar system. The data were collected as part of Operation IceBridge funded aircraft survey campaigns.
